\par\plain {\f6\fs24\b1\i0\cf1 Start with: I did a lot of normal stuff, as well. Was built as a fairly standard AI bot with distributed systems (see chapter 2) with reactions, drives, sensors etc. A little more about the build and project and what is }{\f7\fs24\b1\i1\cf1 regular}{\f6\fs24\b1\i0\cf1  about it. How did I use autocosmic ideas?}
